OL,3,CHigh street businesses left underwater
OL,4,Cas River Monnow bursts its banks
OL,6,FHigh street businesses in Monmouth
OL,7,Fhave been flooded after the nearby
OL,8,Friver burst its banks overnight.
OL,10,FSouth Wales Fire and Rescue declared a
OL,11,Fmajor incident in Monmouth in the
OL,12,Fearly hours of Saturday following
OL,13,F"severe and widespread" flooding
OL,14,Facross the town and surrounding
OL,15,Fcommunities.
OL,17,FEmergency crews were called to the
OL,18,Fscene to provide additional support,
OL,19,Fincluding police and ambulance,
OL,20,Fmountain rescue and coastguard workers.
