OL,3,CHigh street businesses left underwater
OL,4,Cas River Monnow bursts its banks
OL,6,FSome were left trapped inside their
OL,7,Fbusinesses overnight as flood waters
OL,8,Fswept through their front doors.
OL,10,FArea Manager Matt Jones said
OL,11,Fconditions remained challenging due to
OL,12,Ffast-moving water, blocked roads and
OL,13,Fpressure on infrastructure.
OL,15,FHe said: "This is a large-scale
OL,16,Fincident, and our crews and partners
OL,17,Fhave been working tirelessly through
OL,18,Fthe night and into today to help those
OL,19,Faffected.
