OL,4,Cas River Monnow bursts its banks
OL,6,F"I want to thank everyone involved for
OL,7,Fthe professionalism and care they
OL,8,Fcontinue to show in very difficult
OL,9,Fcircumstances.
OL,11,F"I would urge the public to avoid the
OL,12,FMonmouth area completely where
OL,13,Fpossible. The flooding is significant,
OL,14,Fand we need to keep routes clear to
OL,15,Fallow emergency services to reach the
OL,16,Fpeople who need us most. If you are in
OL,17,Fimmediate danger with threat to life
OL,18,For property, or need urgent
OL,19,Fassistance, please call 999."
